data.title: List of CubeSats
data.meta_description: The following is a list of CubeSats, nanosatellites used primarily by universities for research missions, typically in low Earth orbits. Some CubeSats became their country's first national satellite. The extensive Nanosatellite and CubeSat Database lists nearly 4,000 CubeSats and NanoSats have been launched since 1998. The organization forecasts that 2080 nanosats will launch within the next 6 years.
data.text: The following is a list of CubeSats, nanosatellites used primarily by universities for research missions, typically in low Earth orbits.
